#: APP-MANAGER:1935
msgid " Run the \\\"$AMCLI -h\\\" command to find out more"
msgstr " Pokreni \\\"$AMCLI -h\\\" komandu da saznaš više"

#: APP-MANAGER:1997
msgid "This feature is disabled by your organization"
msgstr "Ova mogućnost je isključena od strane tvoje organizacije"

#: APP-MANAGER:2059
msgid "NAME"
msgstr "IME"

#: APP-MANAGER:2060
msgid "VERSION"
msgstr "VERZIJA"

#: APP-MANAGER:2061
msgid "SYNOPSIS"
msgstr "PREGLED"

#: APP-MANAGER:2062
msgid ""
"DESCRIPTION: A command line utility to install and manage AppImages and "
"other portable programs for GNU/Linux thanks to its AUR-inspired database."
msgstr ""
"OPIS: Komandni program za instaliranje i upravljanje AppImage-ova i ostalih "
"portabilnih programa za GNU/Linux zahvaljujući AUR-inspirisanoj bazi "
"podataka."

#: APP-MANAGER:2063
msgid "OPTION"
msgstr "OPCIJA"

#: APP-MANAGER:2064
msgid "OPTIONS"
msgstr "OPCIJE"

#: APP-MANAGER:2065
msgid "THIRD-PARTY FLAGS"
msgstr "OPCIJE TREĆE STRANE"

#: APP-MANAGER:2066
msgid "Third-party databases"
msgstr "Baze podataka treće strane"

#: APP-MANAGER:2067
msgid "SITES"
msgstr "SAJTOVI"

#: APP-MANAGER:2070
msgid "Description: Shows more info about one or more apps."
msgstr "Opis: Prikazuje više informacija o jednoj ili više aplikacija."

#: APP-MANAGER:2071
msgid ""
"Description: Accede to github APIs using your personal access tokens. The "
"file named \\\"ghapikey.txt\\\" will be saved in $AMDATADIR. Use \\\"del\\\" "
"to remove it."
msgstr ""
"Opis: Pristupi GitHub API-ju koristeći tvoj lični pristupni token (PAT). "
"Fajl po imenu \\\"ghapikey.txt\\\" će biti sačuvan u $AMDATADIR. Koristi \\"
"\"del\\\" da ga obrišeš."

#: APP-MANAGER:2072
msgid ""
"Description: Create a snapshot of the current version of an installed "
"program."
msgstr "Opis: Napravi rezervnu kopiju trenutne verzije instaliranog programa."

#: APP-MANAGER:2073
msgid "Description: Removes all the unnecessary files and folders."
msgstr "Opis: Briše sve nepotrebne fajlove i foldere."

#: APP-MANAGER:2074
msgid ""
"Description: Clone the list of installed apps to an \\\"am-clone.source\\\" "
"file, or search for an existing one on the desktop (priority), in $HOME, or "
"across the entire system and removable devices. Add \\\"-i\\\" or \\"
"\"install\\\" if you want to install or add the listed apps to a new "
"configuration, to share it with anyone on other PCs and configurations. Add "
"the \\\"--system\\\" or \\\"--user\\\" flag if you want all listed apps to "
"be installed system-wide or locally respectively.\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\tYou can also set the path to a custom file by exporting the \\"
"$CLONE_FILE variable."
msgstr ""
"Opis: Kloniraj listu instaliranih aplikacija u \\\"am-clone.source\\\" fajl, "
"ili pretraži postojeći fajl na računaru (prioritet), u $HOME, ili kroz ceo "
"sistem i uklonjive uređaje. Dodaj \\\"-i\\\" ili \\\"install\\\" ako želiš "
"da instaliraš ili dodaš te aplikacije u novu konfiguraciju, da ih podeliš sa "
"ostalima na drugim računarima i konfiguracijama. Dodaj \\\"--system\\\" ili "
"\\\"--user\\\" opciju ako želiš da sve te aplikacije budu instalirane "
"sistemski ili lokalno u skladu sa odabranom opcijom.\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\tTakođe možeš da podesiš putanju do clone fajla tako što izvezeš \\"
"$CLONE_FILE varijablu."

#: APP-MANAGER:2077
msgid ""
"Description: Set a dedicated \\$XDG_CONFIG_HOME for one or more AppImages."
msgstr ""
"Opis: Podesi poseban \\$XDG_CONFIG_HOME direktorijum za jedan ili više "
"AppImage-ova."

#: APP-MANAGER:2078
msgid "Description: Download an older or specific app version."
msgstr "Opis: Preuzmi stariju ili specifičnu verziju aplikacije."

#: APP-MANAGER:2079
msgid ""
"Description: Download one or more installation scripts to your desktop or "
"convert them to local installers for \\\"AppMan\\\". To test the scripts, "
"use the \\\"$AMCLI -i '/path/to/script'\\\" command or enter the directory "
"of the script and run the \\\"$AMCLI -i ./script\\\" command, even using "
"dedicated flags, if necessary (see \\\"-i\\\")."
msgstr ""
"Opis: Preuzmi jednu ili više instalacijsku skriptu na tvoj računar i "
"pretvori ih u lokalni instaler za \\\"AppMan\\\". Kako bi testirao skripte, "
"koristi komandu \\\"$AMCLI -i '/putanja/do/skripte'\\\" ili unesi "
"direktorijum skripte i pokreni \\\"$AMCLI -i ./script\\\" komandu, koristeći "
"posebne opcije ako je potrebno (vidi \\\"-i\\\")."

#: APP-MANAGER:2080
msgid ""
"Description: Install AppImages from github.com, outside the database. This "
"allows you to install, update and manage them all like the others. Where \\"
"\"user/project\\\" can be the whole URL to the github repository, give a "
"name to the program so that it can be used from the command line. "
"Optionally, add an \\\"univoque\\\" keyword if multiple AppImages are listed."
msgstr ""
"Opis: Instaliraj AppImage-ove sa github.com, van baze podataka. Dozvoljava "
"ti da instaliraš, ažuriraš i upravljaš njima kao i sve ostale. Koristi \\"
"\"korisnik/projekat\\\" sintaksu kako bi se dobio ceo URL za GitHub "
"repozitorijum, a zatim unesi ime programa koje bi se koristilo sa terminala. "
"Opciono, dodaj neku unikatnu reč na ime programa ako je AppImage sa istim "
"imenom već instaliran."

#: APP-MANAGER:2081
msgid ""
"Description: Shows the list of all installed programs, with sizes. By "
"default apps are sorted by size, use \\\"--byname\\\" to sort by name. With "
"the option \\\"--less\\\" it shows only the number of installed apps. Option "
"\\\"-fi\\\" only shows installed apps, not the AppImages integrated with the "
"\\\"--launcher\\\" option."
msgstr ""
"Opis: Prikazuje listu svih instaliranih programa, sa veličinama. Fabrički su "
"aplikacije sortirane po veličini, koristi \\\"--byname\\\" kako bi ih "
"sortirao po imenu. Sa opcijom \\\"--less\\\", prikazuje samo broj "
"instaliranih aplikacija. Opcija \\\"-fi\\\" samo prikazuje instalirane "
"aplikacije sa baze podataka, ali ne i AppImage-ove integrisane sa \\\"--"
"launcher\\\" opcijom."

#: APP-MANAGER:2082
msgid "Description: Prints this message."
msgstr "Opis: Prikazuje ovu poruku."

#: APP-MANAGER:2083
msgid ""
"Description: Prevents an installed application from being shown or managed "
"by \\\"$AMCLI\\\"."
msgstr ""
"Opis: Sprečava instaliranu aplikaciju da se prikazuje ili upravlja od strane "
"\\\"$AMCLI\\\"."

#: APP-MANAGER:2084
msgid ""
"Description: Set a dedicated \\$HOME directory for one or more AppImages."
msgstr ""
"Opis: Podesi poseban \\$HOME direktorijum za jedan ili više AppImage-ova."

#: APP-MANAGER:2085
msgid ""
"Description: Set dedicated \\$HOME and \\$XDG_CONFIG_HOME directories for "
"one or more AppImages."
msgstr ""
"Opis: Postavlja posebne \\$HOME i \\$XDG_CONFIG_HOME direktorijume za jedan "
"ili više AppImage-ova."

#: APP-MANAGER:2086
msgid ""
"Description: Allow installed apps to use system icon themes. You can specify "
"the name of the apps to change or use the \\\"--all\\\" flag to change all "
"of them at once. This will remove the icon path from the .desktop file and "
"add the symbolic link of all available icons in the $DATADIR/icons/hicolor/"
"scalable/apps directory. The \\\"--icons\\\" option can be used as \\\"flag\\"
"\" in the \\\"-i\\\" and \\\"-ia\\\" options."
msgstr ""
"Opis: Dozvoli instaliranim aplikacijama da koriste sistemske teme za ikone. "
"Možeš da navedeš ime aplikacije za dozvolu ili koristi \\\"--all\\\" opciju "
"da dozvoliš svim aplikacijama. Ovo će da obriše putanju za ikonu u .desktop "
"fajlu i dodaće simboličnu vezu svih dostupnih ikona u $DATADIR/icons/hicolor/"
"scalable/apps direktorijumu. Opcija \\\"--icons\\\" može da se koristi kao "
"opcija za \\\"-i\\\" i \\\"-ia\\\" opcije."

#: APP-MANAGER:2087
msgid ""
"Description: Install one or more programs or libraries from the list. With "
"the \\\"--debug\\\" option you can see log messages to debug the script. For "
"more details on \\\"--force-latest\\\", see the dedicated option, below. Use "
"the \\\"--icons\\\" flag to allow the program to use icon themes. The \\\"--"
"sandbox\\\" flag allows you to set sandboxes for AppImage packages. It can "
"also be extended with additional flags (see third-party flags, at the bottom "
"of this message)."
msgstr ""
"Opis: Instaliraj jedan ili više programa ili biblioteka sa liste. Sa \\\"--"
"debug\\\" opcijom možeš da vidiš log poruke kako bi otklonio greške sa "
"skripte. Za više detalja o \\\"--force-latest\\\", vidi posebnu opciju "
"ispod. Koristi \\\"--icons\\\" opciju da dozvoliš programu da koristi temu "
"za ikone. Opcija \\\"--sandbox\\\" ti dozvoljava da podesiš sandbox za "
"AppImage programe. Takođe postoje i dodatne opcije (vidi opcije treće strane "
"na dnu ove poruke)."

#: APP-MANAGER:2088
msgid ""
"Description: Same as \\\"install\\\" (see above) but for AppImages only. "
"Option \\\"-ias\\\" (aka Install AppImage & Sandbox) is equivalent to \\\"-"
"ia --sandbox\\\", to set sandboxes for AppImage packages."
msgstr ""
"Opis: Isto kao \\\"install\\\" (vidi iznad), ali samo za AppImage-ove. "
"Opcija \\\"-ias\\\" (takođe poznata i kao Instaliraj AppImage i Sandbox-uj) "
"je jednaka opciji \\\"-ia --sandbox\\\" za podešavanje sandbox-a za AppImage "
"programe."

#: APP-MANAGER:2089
msgid ""
"Description: Shows the list of all the apps available. Without flags only "
"shows the apps in the \\\"AM\\\" database, add the \\\"--appimages\\\" to "
"show only the AppImages or \\\"--portable\\\" to show other formats from the "
"\\\"AM\\\" database. The \\\"--all\\\" flag allows you to consult the set of "
"all supported third-party databases. It can also be extended with additional "
"flags (see third-party flags, at the bottom of this message)."
msgstr ""
"Opis: Prikaži listu svih dostupnih programa. Bez ikakvih opcija prikazuje "
"aplikacije iz \\\"AM\\\" baze podataka. Dodaj \\\"--appimages\\\" kako bi "
"prikazao AppImage-ove ili \\\"--portable\\\" kako bi prikazao ostale formate "
"iz \\\"AM\\\" baze podataka. Opcija \\\"--all\\\" prikazuje listu iz svih "
"podržanih baza podataka, uključujući i treću stranu. Takođe postoje i "
"dodatne opcije (vidi opcije treće strane na dnu ove poruke)."

#: APP-MANAGER:2090
msgid ""
"Description: Prevent an application being updated, if it has an\\\"AM-"
"updater\\\" script."
msgstr ""
"Opis: Spreči ažuriranje aplikacije, ako ima \\\"AM-updater\\\" skriptu."

#: APP-MANAGER:2091
msgid ""
"Description: Set a new default repo, use \\\"add\\\" to append the path to a "
"local directory or an online URL, then use \\\"select\\\" to use it by "
"default, a message will warn you about the usage of this repo instead of the "
"default one. Use \\\"on\\\"/\\\"off\\\" to enable/disable it. Use \\\"purge\\"
"\" to remove all 3rd party repos. Use \\\"info\\\" to see the source from "
"where installation scripts and lists are taken."
msgstr ""
"Opis: Kako bi podesio novi repozitorijum, koristi \\\"add\\\" da dodaš "
"putanju lokalnog direktorijuma ili onlajn URL-a, zatim koristi \\\"select\\"
"\" kako bi ga podesio kao podrazumevanog. Nakon toga ćeš biti obavešten o "
"korišćenju novog repozitorijuma kao podrazumevanog umesto fabričkog. Koristi "
"\\\"on\\\"/\\\"off\\\" da ga uključiš/isključiš. Koristi \\\"purge\\\" da "
"obrišeš sve repozitorijume treće strane. Koristi \\\"info\\\" da vidiš izvor "
"odakle su instalacijske skripte i liste preuzete."

#: APP-MANAGER:2092
msgid ""
"Description: Convert old AppImages and get rid of \\\"libfuse2\\\" "
"dependence."
msgstr ""
"Opis: Pretvori stare AppImage-ove i ukloni zavisnost od \\\"libfuse2\\\" "
"biblioteke."

#: APP-MANAGER:2093
msgid ""
"Description: Overwrite apps with snapshots saved previously (see \\\"-b\\\")."
msgstr ""
"Opis: Zameni aplikacije sa prethodno sačuvanim rezervnim kopijama (vidi \\\"-"
"b\\\")"

#: APP-MANAGER:2094
msgid ""
"Description: Search for keywords in the list of available applications, add "
"the \\\"--appimages\\\" option to list only the AppImages, \\\"--portable\\"
"\" option to list only the portable apps or add \\\"--pkg\\\" to list "
"multiple programs at once. The \\\"--all\\\" flag allows you to consult the "
"set of all supported databases."
msgstr ""
"Opis: Pretraži ključne reči u listi dostupnih aplikacija. Dodaj \\\"--"
"appimages\\\" opciju da vidiš isključivo AppImage-ove, \\\"--portable\\\" "
"opciju da vidiš isključivo portabilne aplikacije ili dodaj \\\"--pkg\\\" da "
"vidiš više tipova programa u isto vreme. Opcija \\\"--all\\\" prikazuje "
"rezultate iz svih podržanih baza podataka."

#: APP-MANAGER:2095
msgid ""
"Description: Reinstall only programs whose installation script has been "
"modified in AM's online database. Use the \\\"--all\\\" flag to reinstall "
"everything instead.\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\tNOTE, this only works with the \\\"AM\\\" database. Apps installed "
"with the \\\"-e\\\" option and custom scripts created with the \\\"-t\\\" "
"option are not supported."
msgstr ""
"Opis: Reinstaliraj isključivo one programe kod kojih se instalacijska "
"skripta izmenila u AM onlajn bazi podataka. Koristi opciju \\\"--all\\\" da "
"reinstaliraš sve.\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\tNAPOMENA, ovo radi isključivo sa \\\"AM\\\" bazom podataka. Aplikacije "
"instalirane sa opcijom \\\"-e\\\" i ručne skripte napravljene sa opcijom \\"
"\"-t\\\" nisu podržane."

#: APP-MANAGER:2098
msgid "Description: Remove and reinstall local/AppMan apps to a new location."
msgstr "Opis: Obriši i reinstaliraj lokalne/AppMan aplikacije u novu lokaciju."

#: APP-MANAGER:2099
msgid "Description: Removes one or more apps, requires confirmation."
msgstr "Opis: Briše jednu ili više aplikacija, zahteva potvrdu."

#: APP-MANAGER:2100
msgid "Description: Removes one or more apps without asking."
msgstr "Opis: Briše jednu ili više aplikacija bez potvrde."

#: APP-MANAGER:2101
msgid ""
"Description: Run an AppImage in a sandbox.\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\tNOTE, \\\"--sandbox\\\" can be used as a flag in \\\"-i\\\" and \\\"-"
"ia\\\" or can be replaced using the option \\\"-ias\\\" (aka Install "
"AppImage & Sandbox)."
msgstr ""
"Opis: Pokreni AppImage u sandbox-u.\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\tNAPOMENA, \\\"--sandbox\\\" može da se koristi kao opcija u \\\"-i\\\" "
"i \\\"-ia\\\" ili može da se koristi opcija \\\"-ias\\\" (takođe poznata i "
"kao Instaliraj AppImage i Sandbox-uj)"

#: APP-MANAGER:2104
msgid "Description: Updates this script to the latest version hosted."
msgstr "Opis: Ažurira ovu skriptu na poslednju verziju."

#: APP-MANAGER:2105
msgid ""
"Description: Generate a custom installation script. To test the scripts, use "
"the \\\"$AMCLI -i '/path/to/script'\\\" command or enter the directory of "
"the script and run the \\\"$AMCLI -i ./script\\\" command, even using "
"dedicated flags, if necessary (see \\\"-i\\\")."
msgstr ""
"Opis: Generiši ručnu instalacijsku skriptu. Kako bi testirao skripte, "
"koristi komandu \\\"$AMCLI -i '/path/to/script'\\\" ili unesi direktorijum "
"skripte i pokreni komandu \\\"$AMCLI -i ./script\\\", koristeći posebne "
"opcije ako je to potrebno (vidi \\\"-i\\\")."

#: APP-MANAGER:2106
msgid ""
"Description: Download and set one or more language packs (if available), set "
"\\\"$AMCLI\\\" to English (default), your language or other languages."
"\\n\\nVisit https://github.com/ivan-hc/AM/tree/$AMBRANCH/translations to get "
"source files needed to submit new translations or to improve the existing "
"ones."
msgstr ""
"Opis: Preuzmi i podesi jedan ili više skup jezika (ako je dostupno). Podesi "
"\\\"$AMCLI\\\" na engleski jezik (podrazumevano), tvoj jezik ili ostale "
"jezike.\\n\\nPoseti https://github.com/ivan-hc/AM/tree/$AMBRANCH/"
"translations kako bi preuzeo izvorne fajlove potrebne za podnošenje novih "
"prevoda ili poboljšavanje postojećih."

#: APP-MANAGER:2107
msgid ""
"Description: Allow a hidden app to be shown and managed again (nulls \\"
"\"hide\\\")."
msgstr ""
"Opis: Dozvoli skrivenoj aplikaciji da bude prikazana i upravljana ponovo "
"(anulira \\\"hide\\\")."

#: APP-MANAGER:2108
msgid ""
"Description: Unlock updates for the selected program (nulls \\\"lock\\\")."
msgstr ""
"Opis: Otključaj ažuriranja za odabarani program (anulira \\\"lock\\\")."

#: APP-MANAGER:2109
msgid ""
"Description: Update everything. Add \\\"--apps\\\" to update only the apps "
"or write only the apps you want to update by adding their names. Add the \\"
"\"--debug\\\" flag to view the output of AM-updater scripts. Add the \\\"--"
"launcher\\\" flag to try to update only local AppImages integrated with the "
"\\\"--launcher\\\" option (see \\\"--launcher\\\")."
msgstr ""
"Opis: Ažuriraj sve. Dodaj \\\"--apps\\\" da ažuriraš isključivo aplikacije "
"ili unesi ime aplikacija za njihovo zasebno ažuriranje. Dodaj opciju \\\"--"
"debug\\\" da uvidiš dodatne poruke AM-updater skripti. Dodaj opciju \\\"--"
"launcher\\\" kako bi pokušao da ažuriraš isključivo lokalne AppImage-ove "
"integrisane sa opcijom \\\"--launcher\\\" (vidi \\\"--launcher\\\")."

#: APP-MANAGER:2110
msgid "Description: Shows the version."
msgstr "Opis: Prikazuje verziju."

#: APP-MANAGER:2111
msgid "Description: Undo \\\"--devmode-enable\\\" (see below)."
msgstr "Opis: Anulira \\\"--devmode-enable\\\" (vidi ispod)."

#: APP-MANAGER:2112
msgid "Description: Use the development branch (at your own risk)."
msgstr ""
"Opis: Koristi programersku brašu - programerski režim (na sopstvenu "
"odgovornost)"

#: APP-MANAGER:2113
msgid "Description: Disable notifications during apps update."
msgstr "Opis: Isključi obaveštenja prilikom ažuriranja aplikacija."

#: APP-MANAGER:2114
msgid "Description: Disable the sandbox for the selected app."
msgstr "Opis: Isključi sandbox za odabranu aplikaciju."

#: APP-MANAGER:2115
msgid ""
"Description: Enable notifications during apps update (nulls \\\"--disable-"
"notifications\\\")."
msgstr ""
"Opis: Uključi obaveštenja prilikom ažuriranja aplikacija (anulira \\\"--"
"disable-notifications\\\")."

#: APP-MANAGER:2116
msgid ""
"Description: Downgrades an installed app from pre-release to \\\"latest\\\"."
msgstr ""
"Opis: Smanjuje verziju instalirane aplikacije iz pre-release u \\\"latest\\"
"\"."

#: APP-MANAGER:2117
msgid ""
"Description: Drag/drop one or more AppImages in the terminal and embed them "
"in the apps menu and customize a command to use from the CLI.\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\tNOTE that \\\"--launcher\\\" can be used as a flag in \\\"-u\\\" to "
"try to update the integrated AppImages (see \\\"-u\\\"). This works only if "
"\\\"appimageupdatetool\\\" is installed and delta updates are supported. "
"This flag does not work miracles, I strongly suggest to use options \\\"-ia\\"
"\" and \\\"-e\\\" instead."
msgstr ""
"Opis: Drag/drop-uj jedan ili više AppImage-ova u terminal i ugradi ih u "
"aplikacijski meni i prilagodi komandu za korišćenje u terminalu.\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\tNAPOMENA da \\\"--launcher\\\" može da se koristi kao opcija u \\\"-u\\"
"\" radi ažuriranja integrisanih AppImage-ova (vidi \\\"-u\\\"). Ovo radi "
"isključivo ako je \\\"appimageupdatetool\\\" instaliran i ako su delta "
"ažuriranja podržana. Ova opcija ne čini čuda, te strogo preporučujem da se "
"umesto ovoga koriste opcije \\\"-ia\\\" i \\\"-e\\\"."

#: APP-MANAGER:2120
msgid ""
"Description: Switch \\\"AM\\\" back to \\\"AM\\\" from \\\"AppMan Mode\\"
"\" (see \\\"--user\\\")."
msgstr ""
"Opis: Vrati \\\"AM\\\" nazad u sistemski \\\"AM režim\\\" iz lokalnog \\"
"\"AppMan režima\\\" (vidi \\\"--user\\\")."

#: APP-MANAGER:2121
msgid ""
"Description: Made \\\"AM\\\" run in \\\"AppMan Mode\\\", locally, useful for "
"unprivileged users. This option only works with \\\"AM\\\".\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\tThe \\\"--user\\\" option can also be used just as a flag for "
"installation options. For example:\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t- Use it to install applications locally, option \\\"-i\\\" or \\"
"\"install\\\":"
msgstr ""
"Opis: Učini da \\\"AM\\\" bude pokrenut u lokalnom \\\"AppMan Režimu\\\", "
"korisno za neprivilegovane korisnike. Ova opcija radi isključivo sa \\\"AM\\"
"\".\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\tOpcija \\\"--user\\\" takođe može da se koristi kao opcija za "
"instalacije. Na primer:\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t- Za instaliranje aplikacija lokalno, koristi opciju \\\"-i\\\" ili \\"
"\"install\\\":"

#: APP-MANAGER:2126
msgid "- Also suboptions of \\\"-i\\\" can work with this flag:"
msgstr "- Takođe podopcije od \\\"-i\\\" mogu da rade sa ovom opcijom:"

#: APP-MANAGER:2127
msgid ""
"- Same for AppImages only, option \\\"-ia\\\" or \\\"install-appimage\\\":"
msgstr ""
"- Isto za isključivo AppImage-ove, opcija \\\"-ia\\\" ili \\\"install-"
"appimage\\\":"

#: APP-MANAGER:2128
msgid ""
"- External AppImages can be installed like this as well, option \\\"-e\\\" "
"or \\\"extra\\\":"
msgstr ""
"- Eksterni AppImage-ovi takođe mogu da budu instalirani na ovakav način, "
"opcija \\\"-e\\\" ili \\\"extra\\\":"

#: APP-MANAGER:2129
msgid ""
"NOTE, \\\"AM\\\" 9 or higher is also able to update and manage apps locally, "
"by default, and without having to switch to \\\"AppMan Mode\\\"."
msgstr ""
"NAPOMENA, \\\"AM\\\" verzija 9 ili više je takođe sposoban da ažurira i "
"upravlja aplikacijama lokalno bez potrebe da se menja u \\\"AppMan Režim\\\"."

#: APP-MANAGER:2496
msgid ""
